      "navigationShell": "280px sidebar (brand area + 7 nav items with data-nav-key + MCP status footer + settings entry) + topbar (pageTitle + pageSubtitle + action group with search field + buttons); sidebar and topbar share the same warm parchment surface; content area is a scrollable grid region below topbar",
